Recommends: nos-web
Description: NithronOS Update Service
 Manages atomic system updates with automatic rollback capabilities.
 Provides signed APT repository management, Btrfs snapshot-based
 rollback, and safe update application with postflight checks.
 .
 Features:
  - Multiple update channels (stable/beta)
  - Automatic rollback on failure
  - Btrfs snapshot management
  - GPG signature verification
  - Progress tracking and streaming
